         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>In the excellent day in which the Jovian year Caṟucitti, which occurs in the Caka
               year 1630, the month of Āvaṇi, the first day, Friday, the bright fortnight, the
               fourteenth [lunar day], the constellation of Pūcam come together, the Kantappurāṇam
               was fully copied and completed for the mutt (maṭam) of Mr Citamparaiyar of
               Melaipāṭṭāmpākkam. This is the handwriting of Cuppiṟamaṇiya Tampirāṉ.</p>
         </div>
